game.name: Ice Princess In NYC
game.description:
Your favorite frozen queen Elsa has got bored living in her ice-made castle. Meanwhile, Anna visited her home and advised her to travel a bit to change her mood. This gorgeous princess has now decided to fly to NYC. Oh no! It is the first time when she wants to pack her back for a long outing in another place so she gets confused what to shop for the first trip of her life. Join Elsa In NYC and be prepared to become a partner of her short shopping spree!

She relies on your amazing fashion sense so feel free to pick up the items you like. Make sure to help the girl to choose a modern outfit when you shop with her in this HTML5 shopping game. Give your girl a trendy bodycon outfit, a two-piece dress of your choice, or some lovely fit and flare outfits! Mix and match as many dresses as you can to decide which would look awesome on her! Do not forget to accessorize her dress with a matching leather handbag, designer sunglasses or an elegant hair accessory.

Hey girls! Many popular beauty salons are also there to explore when you reach the New York so also take her to get a complete makeover. You can help her to enjoy a refreshing facial treatment under the guidance of the highly experienced and most talented New York beauticians. Guide her to reach the widely renowned Starbucks to enjoy a wonderful ice coffee! Have a blast in our other popular girls games and enjoy with your friends on atmegame.com no download required!
